title: BRIEF-OEM Q3 operating profit rises
text:
BRIEF-OEM Q3 operating profit rises 
Oct 20 (Reuters) - 
* OEM International Q3 incoming orders rose 14% to SEK 517 million (453) 
* OEM International Q3 operating profit (EBITA) rose 21% to sek 65 million (54) 
* Net sales rose 18% to SEK 530 million (448) Source text for Eikon: Trending On Reuters
